{"tid":1986822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【理大衝突】駕車衝警防線認罪 裝修工判囚5個月2周","createTime":"2020-04-24T05:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T06:11:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec41a78d3b964624a6011c9f0ea63896407f5d33","tid":1986822,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"去年11月中旬大批市民前往聲援在圍困理工大學的示威者，期間有私家車衝向警員防線，險象環生，警員鳴槍兩次警告，私家車司機當日成功駛離現場，但近半個月後再駕駛時被捕，更被揭發其「學神牌」早已失效。他今在九龍城法院承認無牌駕駛、危險駕駛等8項罪名。辯方求情指被告當日因好奇而駛近至理大附近，但就怕被人發現自己無牌駕駛，才會發生本案。裁判官判刑前告誡被告既已為人父，理應考慮到無牌及危駕影響很大，望他引以為戒，判囚5個月2星期，停牌1年。<br />\n<br />\n28歲被告湯昌隆，為二手貨物買賣自僱人士，他今承認2項無牌駕駛罪、2項沒有第三者保險而駕駛罪，以及1項危險駕駛罪。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告於去年11月16日成功出售涉案私家車，翌日則向新車主表示，有朋友出售的避震或適合該白色私家車，於是借車到尖沙咀試車。同日有警員在柯士甸道近漆咸道南作查封，被告當時沿柯士甸道向西行，撞破查封膠紙，被告繼續駛至柯士甸道152號始停下。<br />\n<br />\n警員上前調查時，被告突將車向前衝，幾乎撞到警員。警員避開後警告被告，但被告又突然加速衝向警員，另一警員見狀於是鳴槍警示，射中私家車擋風玻璃，而差點被撞的警員亦曾發射橡膠子彈。被告於翌日始將車歸還新車主。警方調查後得悉被告為肇事司機，於12月2日在上海街截獲並拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1754544/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%A7%95%E8%BB%8A%E8%A1%9D%E8%AD%A6%E9%98%B2%E7%B7%9A%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A5%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%882%E5%91%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1754544%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%25A7%2595%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A1%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%25B7%259A%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A5%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%25882%25E5%2591%25A8&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=1bd9d66b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1754544%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%25A7%2595%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A1%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%25B7%259A%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A5%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%25882%25E5%2591%25A8&h=92aebb97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1754544/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%A7%95%E8%BB%8A%E8%A1%9D%E8%AD%A6%E9%98%B2%E7%B7%9A%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A5%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%882%E5%91%A8</a>"},{"pid":"0fd62438a6cc8e1d9c43be93e77eaf00d87f661f","tid":1986822,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6459d500f14c46c502b6b8eba0120e89414ee78b","tid":1986822,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"好勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd23b1bf3e572ac9e02991332284d9d578676f7","tid":1986822,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e27562ec53300f416c96cfddcd4328b23c8d3d2","tid":1986822,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"手足還押差唔多五個月<br />\n扣除假期應該今日放得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}